Ecross使用「叉00S」架設網站。

===Login notification===
  -include\checkLogin.php:  used loginMailer to send email
  -class\loginMailer.php :  class to send email after login
  -language\tchinese_utf8\mail_template\loginFail.tpl   :   mail template
  -language\tchinese_utf8\mail_template\loginSuccess.tpl:   mail template
  -language\english\mail_template\loginFail.tpl         :   mail template
  -language\english\mail_template\loginSuccess.tpl      :   mail template

===Group notification===
  -include\checkLogin.php:  restore SESSION and redirect.
  -include\common.php    :  set letAnonymousPass.
